{"type": "article", "id": 17708, "title": "放笔记本的折叠桌面", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-18T06:40:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 98, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134831cfyGeAPIidSta7MV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个专门放笔记本的折叠桌面，专为办公室人群设计。折叠之前，它是一个笔记本的保护壳，按照纹路交叉旋转后可以成为一个立体的台面，方便久坐的人站起来使用。如果遇到过矮茶几，也能帮你调整视线，更舒服地使用电脑。它是用压克力帆布做的，有大小三种型号，目前正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1459624267/levit8-the-first-truly-portable-standing-desk\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134830h1ga2m5Hbji9eIXT.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"378\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55588235\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144845p9y0UxJDlmqz6MnX.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144845QZUvmWhGK8Lc0opN.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144846Qun5THkxab3otwBG.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144846eNLh0mf4gP5RwiVE.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"454\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}